<L>__{interior backstage corridor vienna night 1780's}
<C>__{madame weber}
<D>__{let us pass, please! let us pass at once! we're with the emperor.}
<C>__{flunky}
<D>__{i am sorry, madame. it is not permitted.}
<C>__{madame weber}
<D>__{do you know who i am?}
<P>__{(pointing to constanze)}
<D>__{this is my daughter. i am frau weber. we are favoured guests!}
<C>__{flunky}
<D>__{i am sorry, madame, but i have my orders.}
<C>__{madame weber}
<D>__{call herr mozart! you call herr mozart immediately! this is insupportable!}
<C>__{constanze}
<D>__{mother, please!}
<C>__{madame weber}
<D>__{go ahead, constanze. just ignore this fellow.}
<P>__{(pushing her)}
<D>__{go ahead, dear!}
<C>__{flunky}
<P>__{(barring the way)}
<D>__{i am sorry, madame, but no! i cannot let anyone pass.}
<C>__{madame weber}
<D>__{young man, i am no stranger to theatres. i'm no stranger to insolence!}
